c: 14
v: 44
t: "Era tiisa abantu olunaku ebibonerezo lwe biribajjira, abo abeeyisa obubi nebagamba nti ayi Mukama omulabirizi waffe, tulindirize okumala akaseera katono tusobole okwanukula okukoowoola kwo era tugoberere ababaka, (baligamba) abaffe temwalayira oluberyeberye nti temugenda kuva ku nsi"